OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud. There will
OL,7,Fbe some bright or sunny spells through
OL,8,Fthe day. Light west to northwesterly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud and clear spells.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FDry with some sunshine,
OL,17,Fperhaps some low cloud around the
OL,18,FShetland coast. Quite warm across
OL,19,Fwestern parts of Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
